00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,840
So this is a way of saying that I'm really busy.
这是一种表达“我真的很忙”的方式。

166
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:00,840
Charles Really busy.
Charles 真的很忙。

167
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:02,200
I'm really tired of it.
我真的厌倦了。

168
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:03,200
All right.
好的。

169
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:07,000
