I'm going to my anthro class.
我要去上人类学课了。

242
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:55,960
We've been focusing on Darwin all term since it's the 200th anniversary of his birth or
这学期我们一直在讲达尔文，因为今年是他诞辰200周年，还是

